          <Vi>thuộc về Việt Nam, người Việt Nam, hoặc tiếng Việt</Vi>
          <En>Relating to Vietnam, its people, or its language.</En>
          <Example>She studies Vietnamese literature and history.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="f752ec59-21ab-4aa8-9cc3-9069c022cf21">
